{"tid":2462473,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球首間NFT房屋以288枚以太幣售出 　約值50萬美元","createTime":"2021-03-26T04:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T07:15:50.000Z","uid":66271,"like":51,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"51feed8a9db25b6ceb437f69dceb5aa678462fba","tid":2462473,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915082/20210324_nft_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915082%2F20210324_nft_1024.jpg&h=2536c352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加密貨幣投資熱潮未減，虛擬資產近月被炒起，其中，區塊鏈發行的數碼資產「非同質化代幣」（Non-Fungible Token，NFT）備受投資者追捧。繼本月國際拍賣行佳士得（Christie's）首次以NFT形式拍賣純數碼藝術作品，以天價5.4億美元售出後，全球首宗NFT數字房屋亦在本月內以288枚以太幣成功拍賣，約值50萬美元（約388.5萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，該數字房屋名為「火星屋」（Mars House），由當代藝術家Krista Kim創建。Krista Kim指，買家可上載「火星屋」檔案到名為「元宇宙」的虛擬世界（metaverse）中，並體驗該數字房地產。她預計，NFT交易未來將會在短時間內融入現實的生活方式中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915082/nft_groupphoto01_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915082%2Fnft_groupphoto01_1024.PNG&h=4600e528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNFT是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\nNFT（Non-Fungible Token）是以區塊鏈技術產生的獨有標記，可用作認證虛擬資產物主的擁有權。以圖片為例，在互聯網世界中，網民可把電子圖片任意另存作為己用，因此，當人們交易某張電子圖片時，便會以NFT作為憑證，表示自己是該物品的主人。<br />\n<br />\nNFT形式不限，可以是靜態的網上圖片、遊戲道具、數碼藝術品，也可以是動態的影片。比如Twitter（美﹕TWTR）行政總裁Jack Dorsey先前便把他在Twitter上首篇帖文的擁有權以NFT形式出售，叫價290萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915082/gucci_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915082%2Fgucci_1024.PNG&h=375e8630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNFT市場可謂有價有市，Gucci今年便順應潮流，推出首款虛擬球鞋，每對售價12美元。Tesla（美﹕TSLA）創辦人Elon Musk 上周曾在社交網站Twitter表示，擬把一首關於NFT的歌以NFT形式出售，惟昨日（23日）他突然表示，感覺「有點不對勁」，將不會出售該首歌曲。"},{"pid":"a8fcbfdcbbab4e1c67d3ec081d0b09cac7b42c33","tid":2462473,"uid":23407,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔： scam"},{"pid":"e93bd5c3b3e518771996908c703ced9199caffee","tid":2462473,"uid":113000,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"sims 屋都值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db64b2bcb699232db781a379fc7316bce6419669","tid":2462473,"uid":128117,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"地球online 寶物交易"},{"pid":"e1d129dc36c532c80f23bf99f8f21df0b19b4b2a","tid":2462473,"uid":139103,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"為炒而炒，爆煲近了。下一次幣災將由NFT引爆"},{"pid":"e751064732e1b3743522cbc127ced0d2a4d5347a","tid":2462473,"uid":72241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1d129dc36c532c80f23bf99f8f21df0b19b4b2a","tid":2462473,"uid":139103,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"為炒而炒，爆煲近了。下一次幣災將由NFT引爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"又講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec96e089a8f91df38c9014bbbc86c57f7be9b5ea","tid":2462473,"uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e1d129dc36c532c80f23bf99f8f21df0b19b4b2a","tid":2462473,"uid":139103,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"為炒而炒，爆煲近了。下一次幣災將由NFT引爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"然後直上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9ee275a55d24b383596ea3338167b072d3832e","tid":2462473,"uid":71279,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"虛擬鞋有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90a7cc71fef9337bf6